        <div id="FAid"><h3>First Aid</h3>

        <br>

            
            <p>When someone is being treated for cancer, really there is no first aid to render.  </p>

            <p>Instead we can supply “Emotional first aid”. The best thing that we must give them is our emotional care, patience and understanding. Cancer patients may exhibit many feelings like anger, fear, stress, depression, loneliness and sadness.</p>
            <p>  So it is very important to understand the patients’ feelings and treat them with kindness and understanding. Loss of appetite is also a symptom that can be commonly seen among cancer patients. So it’s better if we can serve them with foods look appealing and hopefully the patient will be able to eat.</p>

