        <div id="Prec"><h3>Precautions</h3>

            <br>

        <img src="cancerremediesinfo.jpg">

        <br>

           <p>If someone is concerned about cancer prevention there are some simple lifestyle facts to change. </p>

            <p>Any kind of a tobacco using puts you in trouble with cancer and it is linked with various types of cancer such as cancer of the lung, mouth, throat, larynx, bladder and kidney. Even if someone breaths the second hand smoke can also increase the risk of lung cancer. So anyone can reduce the risk of cancer mainly by quitting tobacco.</p>

            <p>Foods can also reduce the risk of cancer. By eating plenty of fruits and vegetables, eating fewer high calorie foods, limiting processed meats, using olive oil over butter and fish instead of red meat, eating more and more plant based foods can reduce the risk of cancer.</p>

            <p>Always try to keep a healthy weight and be physically active. You must include at least 30 minutes of physical activity in your daily routine.<p>

